## REG_SCRIPT — Logica de Execucao (XML)

O Script XML define a logica real que sera executada. Codificado em base64 **SEM null padding**.

**CRITICO: O Script DEVE usar line endings CRLF (`\r\n`).** Mesmo requisito do DFM.

### Encoding

```python
def encode_script_b64(text: str) -> str:
    crlf = text.replace("\r\n", "\n").replace("\n", "\r\n")
    data = crlf.encode("iso-8859-1")
    return base64.b64encode(data).decode("ascii")
```

### Estrutura XML do Script

```xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="ISO-8859-1"?>
<RULE ID="ID" NAME="Nome&#x20;do&#x20;Fluxograma" COMPONENTNAME="FlowStart1"
      DESCRIPTION="Inicio" DEBUG="FALSE">
  <HEADER>
    <AUTHOR>master</AUTHOR>
    <DATE>DD/MM/AAAA HH:MM:SS</DATE>
    <RANKING>10,0</RANKING>
  </HEADER>
  <PARAM TYPE="Tipo" SIZE="">nomeParam</PARAM>
  <VAR TYPE="Tipo" SIZE="">nomeVar</VAR>
  <DECLARERETURN TYPE="" SIZE=""/>
  <ACTION>
    <!-- passos do fluxograma -->
  </ACTION>
</RULE>
```

**NAO usar** atributos/tags como `AIGENERATED`, `AIPROMPT`, `CODE` — nao existem no formato real.

### Elementos do ACTION

#### EXPRESSION — Chamada de funcao

```xml
<EXPRESSION RETURN="varRetorno" COMPONENTNAME="flowExpression1"
            DESCRIPTION="Descricao do passo">
  <FUNCTION NAME="Nome Amigavel" REALNAME="ebfNomeFuncao">
    <PARAMS>
      <VARIABLE NAME="param1"/>
      <CONSTANT TYPE="Letras" NULL="FALSE">valor</CONSTANT>
    </PARAMS>
  </FUNCTION>
</EXPRESSION>
```

#### DECISION — Condicional

```xml
<DECISION COMPONENTNAME="FlowDecision1" DESCRIPTION="Condicao?">
  <CONDITION>
    <FUNCTION NAME="Igual" REALNAME="isEqual">
      <PARAMS>
        <VARIABLE NAME="var1"/>
        <CONSTANT TYPE="Letras" NULL="FALSE">valor</CONSTANT>
      </PARAMS>
    </FUNCTION>
  </CONDITION>
  <IFTRUE>
    <ACTION>
      <!-- passos se verdadeiro -->
    </ACTION>
  </IFTRUE>
  <IFFALSE>
    <ACTION>
      <!-- passos se falso -->
    </ACTION>
  </IFFALSE>
</DECISION>
```

#### REMARK — Conector/Juncao

Usado quando um FlowConnector junta dois caminhos:

```xml
<REMARK COMPONENTNAME="FlowConnector1"></REMARK>
```

#### REFERENCE — Referencia a componente ja definido

Quando o mesmo componente (ex: FlowEnd1) e alcancado por dois caminhos diferentes:

```xml
<REFERENCE COMPONENTNAME="FlowEnd1"/>
```

#### CALLRULE — Chamada a outro fluxograma

```xml
<CALLRULE ID="ID_REGRA" NAME="Nome Sub Fluxo" RETURN="varRetorno"
          PARAMSCOUNT="N" COMPONENTNAME="FlowSubRoutine1"
          DESCRIPTION="Descricao">
  <PARAMS>
    <VARIABLE NAME="paramValue"/>
  </PARAMS>
</CALLRULE>
```

#### RULERETURN — Fim do fluxo

```xml
<RULERETURN COMPONENTNAME="FlowEnd1" DESCRIPTION="Fim">
</RULERETURN>
```

